# JQuery Dapper Select

A degradable method for overlaying a `<select>` input with a `<span>` element.

## Usage
#### Javascript
	$('select').dapperSelect();
#### CSS
	.dapper-select {
	  background: red;
	}
	.dapper-select.changed {
	  background: yellow;
	}
	.dapper-select-inner {
	  background: url('canvas-list-nav-item-arrow-.gif') no-repeat center right;
	}


### Code originally from
<http://www.adamcoulombe.info/lab/jquery/select-box/>

